data.description: PRICED BELOW MARKET VALUE!!!!!    Welcome home to this 3-bedroom 2 bath home in a great location! The home features a fenced in back yard, recessed lighting all in a nice split floor plan! In addition to the three bedrooms the home also features a den/office plus a dining area giving you plenty of space for all of your needs! The master bathroom boasts a large garden tub, a standalone shower and two closets! The AC is less than a year old, internet and Cable included in the HOA FEE! Quiet and established neighborhood only a short distance from the local Poinciana Community Park! Book your showing today to make this home yours! While all info is deemed to be accurate and correct, buyer to verify all information to include measurements regarding home is true and accurate prior to purchase, home sold AS-IS.
